overview.en: Hongmen Token Project introduction:  Global Hongmen Community is a global virtual community based on the long history, wide coverage and influence of

brand, more than 30 million basic members and a large number of new members. Global Hongmen Community provides a reliable credit recognition system for all Chinese and provides a wide range of exchanges. Mutual aid platform has broad development space.
        The Hongmen Token (HMT) is formally based on the global Hongmen community's extensive application scenarios, good circulation and the development of digital tokens, supply ceiling of 10 billion. Efforts should be made to create a digital asset ecosystem for centralization, ease of use and service to global users.
overview.zh:
洪门令牌（HMT）项目简介: 全球洪门社区是基于“洪门”品牌悠久的历史、全球广泛的覆盖面和影响力，3000万以上的基础会员和大批新增会员而建成的全球性虚拟社区，全球洪门社区为全体华人提供了可以信赖的信誉认可体系，提供了可以进行广泛交流互助的平台，因此拥有广阔的发展空间。
        洪门令牌（HMT）正式基于全球洪门社区广泛的应用场景，良好的流通性而开发的数字代币，供应上限为100亿个。努力打造去中心化、安全易用、服务全球用户的数字资产生态圈。
